{"tid":2373760,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Cyberpunk 2077》遊戲售價大幅減價 50%","createTime":"2021-01-20T16:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T21:34:27.000Z","uid":66365,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b88b8a145382a9fe8a26b29e04c6a1a7eb9513","tid":2373760,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"由 CD Projekt Red 製作的《Cyber​​punk 2077》的售價目前己經大幅下跌，作為 2020 年最被期待的遊戲之一，正式發售不到兩個月，由於大量的錯誤和故障，目前售價跌落至 $30 美元，僅佔原始定價的百分之 50。<br />\n<br />\nCD Projekt Red 尚未對此減價發表任何評論，消息人士透露，此價位存在的時間可能不會太久，因為 CD Projekt Red 將在不久後解決種種遊戲中的故障問題，完整應有的遊戲體驗。此外，《Cyber​​punk 2077》還將在今年晚些時候推出免費的 DLC 資源包以及針對 Sony PlayStation 5 和 Microsoft Xbox Series X 的次世代主機升級內容。<br />\n<br />\nCD Projekt Red 的《Cyber​​punk 2077》目前在 Best Buy 和其他指定零售商正以 $30 美元的價格販售中，有興趣個各位不妨即刻入手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑死，班忠粉又要俾人撚一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548cef071a9f81b2610dba05c86bc5babba64620","tid":2373760,"uid":131884,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比返啲錢我"},{"pid":"1cdce0af44435710144e03c93286509ff236589d","tid":2373760,"uid":159313,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"ubi終於搵到對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952141a59bbae8f4c53971477c23ba923fbf0442","tid":2373760,"uid":92401,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"usd30 都覺得貴囉"},{"pid":"479d7a3cde828d213d08b76317894ced6f09722a","tid":2373760,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"